title: Keep fee rises in debate mix: University of Sydney vice-chancellor Michael Spence
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › Keep fee rises in debate mix: Univers... Keep fee rises in debate mix: University of Sydney vice-chancellor Michael Spence 12 hrs ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
The Turnbull government should not be spooked from charging students more to go to university as it tries to break the impasse on fee deregulation, according to the University of Sydney's vice-chancellor. Professor Michael Spence said concern about higher fees ignored the "uncomfortable fact" that many undergraduates come from wealthy backgrounds and attended wealthy private schools.
